# PARTNERSHIPS PAGE
partnerships-header = Mgwirizano
partnerships-header-text = Zimafunika zambiri kuti Common Voice ichitike! Sitichita tokha. Mukufuna kugwirizana nafe? Tikufuna kumva kuchokera kwa inu.
partnerships-get-in-touch = Lumikizanani nafe
partnerships-become-a-partner = Khalani Mnzanu Wogwirizana ndi Mawu
partnerships-community-header = Anthu ammudzi, Opanga Zinthu ndi Anthu Omwe Ali Pagulu
partnerships-community-description = Anthu ammudzi ndi mtima wopambana wa Common Voice - amachokera padziko lonse lapansi, ndipo ndi olimbikitsa zilankhulo, asayansi ndi ojambula. Mutha kuphunzira zambiri za momwe mungachitire nawo patsamba lathu la <about>About</about> komanso mu buku lathu la <community>Community playbook</community>. Ngati mukufuna mgwirizano wozama pakati pa mabungwe, <emailFragment>lumikizani nafe.</emailFragment>
partnerships-foundations-header = Maziko
partnerships-foundations-description = Timagwira ntchito ndi mabungwe, aboma komanso ogwirizana nawo m'madera kuti intaneti ikhale malo abwino, makamaka ku East Africa. Dziwani zambiri za ntchito yathu ya <programmaticWork>yokhudza mapulogalamu.</programmaticWork>
partnerships-governments-header = Maboma
partnerships-governments-description = Tikusangalala kuthandizira kutenga nawo mbali kwa boma pa ukadaulo, luso latsopano komanso ufulu wa zilankhulo. Ngati mukufuna kuyendetsa pulojekiti kapena kampeni yayikulu, chonde lemberani <emailFragment>.</emailFragment>
partnerships-academia-header = Mayunivesite, Maphunziro ndi Ofufuza
partnerships-academia-description = Kupanga zinthu mwanzeru ndi chinthu chofunikira kwambiri pa zomwe timachita. Pa kafukufuku wogwirizana, kusonkhanitsa deta kapena kuyankhulana, <emailFragment>lumikizanani nafe.</emailFragment>
partnerships-small-business-header = Mabizinesi ang'onoang'ono, kuphatikizapo makampani oyambira ukadaulo ndi AI
partnerships-small-business-description = Nthawi zonse timafuna kumva kuchokera kwa ogwiritsa ntchito deta za zosowa zawo ndi momwe akumvera - kuyambira kugwira ntchito limodzi pa nsanja yosonkhanitsira deta mpaka kupereka chidziwitso cha thanzi la deta, tikufuna kumva kuchokera kwa inu.</emailFragment>
partnerships-corporates-header = Makampani akuluakulu ndi makampani okonza mapulani
partnerships-corporates-description = Ngati mukufuna kulankhula zambiri za deta, mukufuna kuyika ndalama pamodzi pakukulitsa nsanja zomwe zakonzedwa kapena kufunafuna mwayi wogwirizana, <emailFragment>tiuzeni.</emailFragment>
partnerships-our-partners = ogwirizana nafe
